# Large per-bar series files (regenerated deterministically by scripts).
# We keep the small summary/ledger/params CSVs in results_*/ tracked
# so the report figures and tables can be regenerated, but the
# per-bar equity & returns series are too big for git.
**/*equity.csv
**/*reference_series.csv
**/*returns.csv

# Large 1-minute data files (regeneratable from upstream provider)
data/*-1minHLV.csv

# Stale exploratory result trees (kept locally but excluded from git)
results_cpp/
results_cpp_official_quick/**/*.csv
results_cpp_smoke/
results_cost_sensitivity_fixed/**/*.csv
results_cpp_fidelity_ty_1m/

# Per-run temp artifacts
*.log
*.tmp
